  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger, cook for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add red bell pepper, chilies, cumin seeds, turmeric powder, and salt. Stir well to combine.",
    "Pour in coconut milk, seal the pressure cooker, and lock the lid in place.",
    "Cook on high pressure for 3 minutes, then release steam naturally (jar will be hot).",
    "Stir gently once before serving with fresh cilantro and lemon juice if desired."
